<section class="page-hero"><div class="sh-container"><div class="sh-eyebrow">FAQ</div><h1 class="sh-h1">How to use the Shadeless 3-Step Serum System</h1><p class="sh-body">Answers about routine order, skin types, Peptisinergix&trade;, ingredients, and orders.</p></div></section>
<section class="sh-section"><div class="sh-container accordion">
  <h2 class="sh-h2">Product Use</h2>
  <details open><summary>What is Shadeless?</summary><div class="content">Shadeless is a biotech skincare brand built around a 3-step serum system for more even-looking tone, smoother-looking texture, and cleaner skin clarity.</div></details>
  <details><summary>What is the 3-Step Serum System?</summary><div class="content">A coordinated routine: Step 1 Prepare, Step 2 Optimize, Step 3 Enhance.</div></details>
  <details><summary>Do I need all three steps?</summary><div class="content">The full system is recommended because each serum has a different role.</div></details>
  <details><summary>How do I use the system?</summary><div class="content">Cleanse, apply Step 1, apply Step 2, apply Step 3, moisturize if needed, and use sunscreen during the day.</div></details>
  <h2 class="sh-h2" style="margin-top:50px;">Skin Type</h2>
  <details><summary>Is Shadeless for all skin tones?</summary><div class="content">Yes. Shadeless is designed for every skin tone. It is not a whitening or bleaching brand.</div></details>
  <details><summary>Can sensitive skin use it?</summary><div class="content">Patch test first and introduce gradually. Discontinue use if irritation occurs.</div></details>
  <details><summary>Should I use sunscreen?</summary><div class="content">Yes. Use sunscreen every morning as the final step of your daytime routine.</div></details>
  <h2 class="sh-h2" style="margin-top:50px;">Science</h2>
  <details><summary>What is Peptisinergix&trade;?</summary><div class="content">Peptisinergix&trade; is Shadeless' formulation philosophy: organizing peptides and active ingredients by role, compatibility, and sequence.</div></details>
  <details><summary>Is Shadeless medical-grade?</summary><div class="content">Shadeless is cosmetic skincare. It is not positioned as a drug, medical treatment, or replacement for dermatological care.</div></details>
</div></section>
